        "action": "Lift the UK visa restrictions placed on Afghan nationals",
        "additional_details": "This is about the humanitarian situation in Afghanistan and concerns about fairness.",
        "background": "I want the UK Government to lift the restrictions on work and student visas for Afghan nationals and ensure that visa decisions are based only on individual assessments rather than nationality.",
